{"id": "art-526", "label": "Art. 526", "title": "Art. 526: Sancţionarea contestatorului de rea-credinţă", "slug": "art-526", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1363509588\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1191\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1363509588\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 526:\nSanc&#355;ionarea contestatorului de rea-credin&#355;&#259; </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1939059147\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1190\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1939059147\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Atunci când contesta&#355;ia a fost f&#259;cut&#259; cu\nrea-credin&#355;&#259;, autorul acesteia poate fi obligat la plata unei amenzi\njudiciare de la 500 lei la 2.000 lei, precum &#351;i, la cererea\np&#259;r&#355;ii interesate, la plata de desp&#259;gubiri pentru repararea\nprejudiciului cauzat prin introducerea contesta&#355;iei.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_126608649\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1189\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_126608649\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Reaua-credin&#355;&#259; rezult&#259; din caracterul\nv&#259;dit nefondat al contesta&#355;iei, precum &#351;i din orice alte\nîmprejur&#259;ri care îndrept&#259;&#355;esc constatarea c&#259; exercitarea\nacesteia s-a f&#259;cut în alt scop decât acela pentru care legea o\nrecunoa&#351;te.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>CARTEA III:Procedura necontencioas&#259;\njudiciar&#259;</span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>TITLUL I:Dispozi&#355;ii generale</span></b></p>"}